國立暨南國際大學化學系教授 (2007-)




Research Interests
I.   Electronically Conducting Materials Controlled synthesis and crystal growth of transition metal oxides with low-dimensional properties that lead to interesting properties such as metal-insulator transition and superconductivity. 
II.  Fast Ionic Conducting Materials  Open framework materials for solid electrodes applied in batteries and electrocatalytic application. Structure design and synthesis of novel compounds are our major interests. 


研究重點
I 電子傳導材料
具有低維度性質的過渡金屬氧化物的合成和晶體   生長，例如具金屬 - 絕緣體轉變和超導性材料。
II快速離子傳導材料
電池和電催化應用中具有開放式框架結構的固體電極材料，新化合物的結構設計和合成是我們的主要興趣。




